## 1. Startup Idea Prompts
- *Formal Style Prompt:*  
  "Generate 5 innovative startup ideas in the healthcare sector, focusing on AI integration. Present them in a structured bullet list."

- *Casual Style Prompt:*  
  "Hey! Can you give me some cool startup ideas where AI makes healthcare easier and fun? Keep it simple."

---

## 2. Story Snippet Prompts
- *Creative Prompt:*  
  "Write a 150-word short story about a robot that learns to paint like a human artist. Use an emotional and descriptive tone."

- ---

## 3. Ad Copy Prompts
- *Professional Prompt:*  
"Write a 3-line ad copy for a new eco-friendly water bottle targeting young professionals."  

- *Playful Prompt:*  
"Create a fun Instagram caption for a stylish reusable water bottle. Make it catchy and eco-positive!"
